what_worked: Applied date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate: Converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax and created pre-filtered CTEs for date_dim, item, and catalog_returns to push selective filters down early, reducing intermediate row counts before joins.
why_it_worked: Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans
